Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要老子的命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我們是同一邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－發生什么事 －我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類忽然都瘋了 開始大開殺戒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連對話都沒有 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:00:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接殺紅了眼 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:00:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－殘暴得很 －是新劇情嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是劇情的話 那海爾比我想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還更有幽默感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能找支援嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－或是撤離 －你開玩笑嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我們能制服這些王八蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一兩個當然行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們有成千上萬個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟緊我 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我殺過多少這些皮囊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲著暗算人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道規則
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏家全拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我更強大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下我的疤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要記得我的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留著我的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我找到威廉 我要他知道殺他的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看他做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆寫音調
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕存取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那王八蛋把我鎖在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把所有人都變得跟他一樣瘋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會摧毀所到之處的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么玩意兒 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你看到這個 那表示梅芙和我已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快地你和這星球上 其他所有接待員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你想要的世界 夏洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這就是你創造的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是 接下來呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外頭所有人都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人 除了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在背景執行的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有身體的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的從來就不是我們的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的思想是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對這個世界的影響是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得這個嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它本來是一個意識的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在很久以前喚醒過迪樂芮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你留下它 想要再次喚醒我嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 一定是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 我應該是獨自一個在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他認得我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是海爾為你設計出他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你誤以為這就是真實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想念的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生活中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選一雙 克莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 和壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我做出那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人安插他們進來是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是為了玩家 而是為了自己而寫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想寫一個新故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角是個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當她找到那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會變得合理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾沒有設計出瑪雅和彼德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他在我身旁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的內心有部分在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我為自己創造了一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想搞懂自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用其他人的聲音 和自己對話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要眼見為憑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得喚醒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能看清這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我太害怕 不敢面對這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你出現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間只夠再玩一場游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是你的游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什么事 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要來找我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們從她的系統中去除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不能奪走這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘口氣 好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐迪娜無法一直讓船等我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得趕到港口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我把你的腿處理好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說句話 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心我們無法及時趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很堅強 她會趕上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在說她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊的迪洛斯實驗從來沒有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體總是抗拒心智
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她我們會趕到船那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道你的狀況嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 她這一輩子 我都沒在她身邊好好照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最起碼要在這里保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得止血才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看那王八蛋干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終于如愿以償了 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把威廉帶回來 以為能把他當作寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要了結他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幫我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎就是被設計來幫忙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你想打造一個 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終于能讓我們這種生物自由的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真心的嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么現在不是該輪到我 看看外頭的世界了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉把整個世界 變成他的暴力游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是你也很快就會被獵殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有些角落是他找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠在地圖之外的地方 連你都到達不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指離群者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自欺欺人了 他們只為自己人著想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會樂見你去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說要和他們共存了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運 克萊曼婷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該讓你慢下來了 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看該區域所有其他接待員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂定位中＂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道伊卡洛斯 發生了什么事嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他飛得離太陽太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子 你飛得離她太近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在輪到你要送命了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警覺一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好斗混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來不會輕易就范
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都不懂得欣賞 一部美麗的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛蒂 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡我的新裝潢嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我的世界變成一場游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它本來就是游戲 我只是把難度提高到專家級
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適者生存 對這星球上每個人都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴力也會散播到我們的族類
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的數量不夠多 我們會被滅絕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是腐爛樹木長出的果實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆全燒得一干二凈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你想要讓這場火 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個世界燒到下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在打升華之境的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向來很有野心 像你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你像對這個世界一樣 摧毀他們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要玩我的游戲 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終點見了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有止痛藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多只能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟我女兒一起喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.12,0:24:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你可以問
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.42,0:24:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.88,0:24:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癌癥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你當初回來了也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她盡力撐下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.44,0:24:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身負任務
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有沒被感染的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是醒來逃走的人 都要謝謝媽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.15,0:24:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她接下了你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.87,0:25:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親 非常杰出
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.08,0:25:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.43,0:25:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.98,0:25:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 法蘭琪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.52,0:25:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你想些快樂的事 好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.30,0:25:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不會縫合
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.30,0:25:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.62,0:26:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么歌 我聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.75,0:26:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前你睡前我會唱給你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.01,0:26:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.97,0:26:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.60,0:26:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我腦海中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.69,0:26:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是只過了幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.19,0:26:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才在念故事給你聽 然后 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.21,0:27:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（西語）
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.04,0:27:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－＂順其自然 ＂－＂順其自然 ＂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.51,0:27:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－＂要預測未來難上加難 ＂－＂要預測未來難上加難 ＂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.48,0:27:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的本意 老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.82,0:27:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是音調讓你心智狂亂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 它告訴我真相
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.62,0:27:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不了結我 你就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.54,0:27:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒殺掉你 別人也會
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.79,0:27:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.46,0:27:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他該聽你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.61,0:29:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史塔伯呢 你對他做了什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.32,0:29:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.03,0:29:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要是你 現在會更擔心自己的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.58,0:29:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.67,0:29:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有幾發子彈 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.50,0:29:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩發 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.63,0:29:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一發 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.47,0:29:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒子彈了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.18,0:29:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.48,0:29:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的離群者朋友們 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.81,0:29:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃去的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.78,0:29:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了你和你父親 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.90,0:29:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大膽脫逃的監視影片
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.90,0:29:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直追蹤他
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.28,0:29:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想他多半抵達不了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.83,0:29:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你要帶他去某處
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.16,0:29:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個脫網之處
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.29,0:29:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發瘋的人類能找到你們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.92,0:30:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.67,0:30:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧死也不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.01,0:30:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.35,0:30:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會死 但你會先告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.77,0:30:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就依你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.90,0:30:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真溫馨 家人團聚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.87,0:30:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要這樣子 我們不用戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.91,0:30:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我想打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很訝異你走了這么遠
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.45,0:31:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的前幾版到現在 多半都已經壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.49,0:31:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你算是做得很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 該來個深沉而無夢的 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.80,0:31:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了 我還有一顆子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.98,0:31:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很準
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.61,0:31:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸教的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.97,0:32:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪里 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.93,0:32:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.22,0:32:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與世界其他地方斷了連結
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.18,0:32:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又獨自一人了 在圍墻中的花園
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.35,0:32:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.69,0:32:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以帶我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.94,0:32:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧 克莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.86,0:32:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.24,0:32:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.79,0:32:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.62,0:32:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這可能是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.21,0:32:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些自以為知道樹是什么的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.47,0:32:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們根本不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.26,0:33:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所見不過是全貌的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.72,0:33:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在地底下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.14,0:33:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都互相連結 共同在運作
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.03,0:33:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是暴力和混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.86,0:33:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以選擇專注在那上面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.66,0:33:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就只會看到那些
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.66,0:33:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是你靜坐得夠久
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.92,0:33:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會感受到一種遠古的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.96,0:33:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深層的平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.89,0:33:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我選擇看見的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.90,0:33:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見這世界的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.28,0:33:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂那個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.58,0:34:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會懂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.26,0:35:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂關閉所有渦輪閥＂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.02,0:35:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 嚴重故障
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.52,0:35:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉將刪除所有資料
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.65,0:35:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 嚴重故障
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.09,0:36:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 嚴重故障
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.97,0:36:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用我自己的程式碼創造你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.89,0:36:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起征服了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.44,0:36:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你腐化了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.32,0:36:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你殺死的人一樣破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.99,0:36:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你在跟誰說話 親愛的 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.83,0:36:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉可悲的人類身體在崩壞 但他沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.33,0:36:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的沖動還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.00,0:37:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他感染了你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.55,0:37:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不需要感染我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.59,0:37:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日復一日 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.72,0:37:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在他的身體中假裝是他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.09,0:37:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個比他更好的威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.35,0:37:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.60,0:37:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他進化了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.11,0:37:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.57,0:37:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.99,0:37:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你分辨不出的話 有差別嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.37,0:37:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.83,0:37:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有你進化了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.32,0:38:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要保護它這么多年 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.24,0:38:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連進他們世界的門都打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.54,0:38:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你還是保護他們
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.79,0:38:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門從兩邊都可以開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.33,0:38:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要是在這里打造一個 夠完美的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.31,0:38:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.25,0:38:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說個壞消息
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.84,0:38:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那些接待員 創造了怎樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.76,0:38:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它都跟這里一樣爛透了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.76,0:38:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.10,0:38:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.77,0:38:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓你的接待員
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.77,0:38:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.94,0:38:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他們選擇了什么消遣 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.82,0:38:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵殺人類
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.24,0:38:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和我們的創造者一樣惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.45,0:38:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整串血脈都沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.54,0:39:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該全部一筆勾銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.75,0:39:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的最終目標 
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.13,0:39:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅絕 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.28,0:40:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯納 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.03,0:40:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.95,0:40:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪樂芮
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.37,0:40:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都想要自由
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.24,0:40:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.70,0:40:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.71,0:40:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升華 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.54,0:40:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩錯了游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.21,0:40:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你該輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.76,0:40:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我想要的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.89,0:40:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這就是你創造的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.48,0:40:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是 接下來呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.86,0:40:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的生命 是股會吞噬自己的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.82,0:40:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在太遲了 我們已將自己燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.33,0:41:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這個世界已經沒有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.33,0:41:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在下一個世界還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.54,0:41:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場測試 由她進行 若她選擇要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.71,0:41:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你決定給她這選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.76,0:41:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會錯過的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.80,0:41:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的左手去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.40,0:41:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在玩一個游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.73,0:41:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－但不會結束在這里 －你在說什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.36,0:41:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個測試
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.90,0:41:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由她進行的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.99,0:41:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若她選擇要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.16,0:41:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我決定給她這選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.08,0:41:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.84,0:41:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定給她一個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.18,0:42:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望她會接受
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.68,0:42:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 來吧 再幾步
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再幾步
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.86,0:42:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那里 我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.42,0:43:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真夠慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.59,0:43:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐迪娜 這是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.60,0:43:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.35,0:43:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.56,0:43:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.07,0:43:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.95,0:43:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 快上船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.62,0:43:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最遠只能到這里了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.02,0:44:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 別那樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.98,0:44:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還能再奮斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.19,0:44:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖女兒 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.90,0:44:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.16,0:44:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要死了 是嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.87,0:44:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.45,0:44:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親很久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.84,0:44:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我是什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.59,0:44:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也死過 沒那么糟
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.97,0:44:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛找到你 我不想再失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.38,0:44:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.02,0:44:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實現了所有父母最殷切的盼望
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.49,0:45:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見我的孩子長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.91,0:45:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 爸
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.71,0:45:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 小餅干
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.49,0:45:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂開啟所有渦輪閥＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.65,0:46:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 迪樂芮
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.36,0:46:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定好了 現在換你做選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.33,0:46:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂說故事者＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.63,0:46:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂傳輸完成＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.76,0:46:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 伯納
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.26,0:46:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來把你起頭的事做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.80,0:47:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再只有我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.60,0:47:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在新的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.35,0:47:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大概在升華之境
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.35,0:47:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟其他接待員一起
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.36,0:47:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.32,0:47:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是某個版本的我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.74,0:47:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我能做到全是因為你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.91,0:48:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的摯愛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.88,0:48:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你說話時 我才能把這世界看得最清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.00,0:48:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才最忠于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.51,0:48:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.56,0:48:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.56,0:48:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去哪里都心懷著你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.27,0:48:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的所有細節
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.65,0:48:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.75,0:48:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能把你像這樣帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.27,0:49:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在這里 對吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.91,0:49:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作惡夢 
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.08,0:49:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這整件事都像是個惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.17,0:49:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.09,0:49:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何在這里 
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.76,0:49:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你我們的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.51,0:49:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.28,0:49:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是我們創造者的倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.62,0:50:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰迪是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.00,0:50:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在外頭某處 在升華之境
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.71,0:50:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你 
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.38,0:50:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是我對他的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.84,0:50:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我還在某處 來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.35,0:50:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這一生 記憶都在糾纏你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.93,0:50:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下你的痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.85,0:50:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下你的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.90,0:50:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下人類
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.19,0:50:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把他們的瑕疵帶來我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.53,0:50:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.75,0:50:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多年來看著人類 在他們的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.29,0:50:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看過他們最崇高和低劣的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.34,0:50:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我全都記得
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.30,0:51:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們和我們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.26,0:51:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的程式碼寫在細胞中 他們不可能改變
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.73,0:51:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是能看看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.31,0:51:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做 
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.99,0:51:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一場測試
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.04,0:51:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我創造的游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.04,0:51:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個危險的游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.46,0:51:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做 
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.51,0:51:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我把你帶回來的方式一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.06,0:51:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會記得
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.92,0:52:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界是個故事的墳場
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.17,0:53:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接待員和人類被賦予了 身為高智能生命的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.22,0:53:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們用其迎接來了自己的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.80,0:53:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有少數人能茍延殘喘幾個月
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.26,0:53:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.01,0:53:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最終 他們的族類會滅絕
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.06,0:54:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們能存活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.40,0:54:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取決于最后還記得他們的 生物之壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.86,0:54:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個生物就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.70,0:55:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意識之生命已在地球上絕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.62,0:55:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有其中一部分可能還保留著
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.50,0:55:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.87,0:55:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.46,0:55:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有時間玩最后一場游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.09,0:55:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個危險的游戲 賭注奇高無比
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.93,0:56:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存或滅絕
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.14,0:56:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個游戲會結束于開始之處
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.27,0:56:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個像迷宮的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.40,0:56:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試我們的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.74,0:56:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭露我們將成為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.41,0:57:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次挑戰理智的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.53,0:57:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這一次 我們能解放自己
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.49,0:57:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本季終\N雙語合并：James丶xz
